{"tid":1776787,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"原來毛記有渣哥49%股份","createTime":"2019-12-09T18:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T06:05:09.000Z","uid":49643,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39b9d7a0ef99834b312adf25b1b5a374a4a1109f","tid":1776787,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"毛記渣哥曾年宵合作推「劣食」攤位<br />\n翻查資料，在翠華入股之初，堅信號只經營3家分店，分別位於銅鑼灣登龍街、深水埗福榮街及大埔。但獲翠華入股後，隨即擴大店舖規模，今年2月及7月已新增兩間分店，分別位於旺角花園街及元朗YOHO MALL，擴至5家分店。<br />\n對比翠華的多品牌發展，以數碼媒體服務為主業的毛記更是「跨界」投資。公司創辦人、控股股東兼執董徐家豪（林日曦）今年初曾披露入股渣哥，雖然當時雙方都未有披露具體條款，但據毛記年報顯示，原來公司是於去年12月31日，以250萬元收購渣哥的49%權益，意味譚小環與丈夫「渣哥」蔡強榮仍為食店大股東。翻查紀錄，毛記與渣哥早有淵源，在2017年已合作在年宵推出「毛記劣食」小食攤位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1575855856514&amp;issue=20191209&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GwBtDYgEDbxrZvBKPF6hhrLetDvqt_jr1HqkMzpqs6dp7JrpFW0TYF6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1575855856514%26issue%3D20191209%26fbclid%3DIwAR2GwBtDYgEDbxrZvBKPF6hhrLetDvqt_jr1HqkMzpqs6dp7JrpFW0TYF6w&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F6jg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=e15f8bdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1575855856514&amp;issue=20191209&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GwBtDYgEDbxrZvBKPF6hhrLetDvqt_jr1HqkMzpqs6dp7JrpFW0TYF6w</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22ea91a01873e7a8895c86f571bf4ab43ec629c","tid":1776787,"uid":213163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T18:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CJS6J8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CJS6J8.jpg&h=459c9125&s={SIZE}\" />唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n好重要聽晚就係啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n【國際人權日．正日集會】<br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權